<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Privacy Policy - <%= appName %></title>
    <meta name="description" content="Privacy Policy for <%= appName %>." />

    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Alfa+Slab+One&family=Vend+Sans:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        :root{
            --bg: #ffffff;
            --card: #ffffff;
            --card2: #f9fafb;
            --border: #e5e7eb;
            --text: #111827;
            --muted: #4b5563;
            --muted2: #6b7280;
            --accent: #2563EB;
            --accent2: #10b981;
            --warn: #f59e0b;
            --shadow: 0 1px 3px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 1px 2px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
            --radius: 12px;
            --mono: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, "Liberation Mono", "Courier New", monospace;
            --sans: 'Vend Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            --display: 'Alfa Slab One', serif;
            --bg-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f4f8 0%, #ffffff 100%);
        }

        * { box-sizing: border-box; }

        body{
            margin:0;
            font-family: var(--sans);
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: var(--text);
            background: var(--bg-gradient);
            background-attachment: fixed;
            padding: 28px 16px 44px;
        }

        a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }
        a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

        .wrap{
            max-width: 940px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .topbar{
            display:flex;
            align-items:center;
            justify-content:space-between;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }

        .brand{
            display:flex;
            align-items:center;
            gap: 12px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .brand:hover{
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .logo{
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
            border-radius: 14px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            background: #f3f4f6;
            display:flex;
            align-items:center;
            justify-content:center;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            flex: 0 0 auto;
        }

        .brandtext{
            display:flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 2px;
            min-width: 0;
        }

        .brand strong{
            font-family: var(--display);
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            letter-spacing: 0.2px;
            color: var(--text);
        }

        .brand span{
            font-size: 0.82rem;
            color: var(--muted2);
        }

        .pill{
            display:inline-flex;
            align-items:center;
            gap:8px;
            padding: 8px 10px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            background: #f3f4f6;
            font-size: 0.86rem;
            color: var(--muted);
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .pill code{
            font-family: var(--mono);
            font-size: 0.82rem;
            color: var(--text);
        }

        .card{
            background: var(--card);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            padding: 30px 28px;
        }

        h1{
            margin: 0 0 8px;
            font-family: var(--display);
            font-size: 2.0rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            color: #111827;
        }

        .meta{
            margin: 0 0 22px;
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        h2{
            margin: 26px 0 8px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            letter-spacing: -0.01em;
            color: #111827;
        }

        p{
            margin: 8px 0 14px;
            color: var(--muted);
        }

        ul{
            margin: 8px 0 14px 18px;
            color: var(--muted);
        }

        li{ margin: 6px 0; }

        .notice{
            border-left: 4px solid var(--accent2);
            background: #f0fdf4;
            padding: 14px 14px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin: 18px 0 22px;
            color: #166534;
        }

        .btn{
            display:inline-flex;
            align-items:center;
            gap: 8px;
            padding: 10px 12px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            background: #f3f4f6;
            color: var(--text);
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.92rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .btn:hover{
            background: #e5e7eb;
            text-decoration: none;
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }

        .footer{
            text-align:center;
            color: var(--muted2);
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            margin-top: 16px;
            padding: 18px 10px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 520px){
            .card{ padding: 22px 16px; }
            h1{ font-size: 1.7rem; }
            .topbar{ flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
<%
const effectiveDate =
        (typeof lastUpdated !== "undefined" && lastUpdated)
                ? lastUpdated
                : new Date().toLocaleDateString();

const gh =
        (typeof githubUrl !== "undefined" && githubUrl)
                ? githubUrl
                : "https://github.com/yourname/yourrepo";

const contact =
        (typeof contactEmail !== "undefined" && contactEmail)
                ? contactEmail
                : null;
%>

<div class="wrap">

    <div class="topbar">
        <a href="/" class="brand">
            <div class="logo">üçΩÔ∏è</div>
            <div class="brandtext">
                <strong><%= appName %></strong>
                <span>Privacy Policy</span>
            </div>
        </a>

        <div class="pill">
            Last updated: <code><%= effectiveDate %></code>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">

        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="meta">
            This Privacy Policy explains how <strong><%= appName %></strong> handles information when you use the App.
            The App is an open-source MCP server designed to help users choose meals randomly.
        </p>

        <div class="notice">
            ‚úÖ <strong>Privacy by Design:</strong>
            <%= appName %> does not collect, sell, or store personal user data on any developer-controlled backend.
        </div>

        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>
            <strong><%= appName %></strong> is intentionally built to minimize data collection.
            The App does not require accounts, registrations, or identifying information.
        </p>

        <ul>
            <li>No names, emails, or user profiles</li>
            <li>No payment information</li>
            <li>No tracking identifiers</li>
            <li>No advertising analytics</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>2. Information Processed During Use</h2>
        <p>
            When you use the App through an AI client such as ChatGPT, the client may send input (for example, a list of meals)
            to the MCP server to generate a response.
        </p>

        <p>
            The App processes this data only transiently in memory to return a meal selection result.
            The developer does not intentionally log or permanently retain this information.
        </p>

        <h2>3. No Data Storage</h2>
        <p>
            The App does not operate a database of user activity and does not store:
        </p>

        <ul>
            <li>chat histories</li>
            <li>personal prompts</li>
            <li>meal preferences</li>
            <li>session identifiers</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>4. Third-Party AI Client Processing</h2>
        <p>
            Your interaction with <%= appName %> is mediated through an AI client platform (such as ChatGPT).
            That platform may collect or retain data according to its own policies.
        </p>

        <p>
            You should review the AI client provider‚Äôs privacy documentation separately, as it governs what happens
            before requests reach the App.
        </p>

        <h2>5. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
        <p>
            The App does not use cookies, trackers, advertising beacons, or analytics services.
        </p>

        <h2>6. Open Source Transparency</h2>
        <p>
            The App is open source, and the full codebase is available publicly at:
        </p>

        <p>
            <a href="<%= gh %>" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                <%= gh %>
            </a>
        </p>

        <p>
            Users are welcome to inspect how the App functions and verify that no hidden data collection occurs.
        </p>

        <h2>7. Children‚Äôs Privacy</h2>
        <p>
            The App is not directed toward children under 13, and the developer does not knowingly collect personal
            data from children.
        </p>

        <h2>8. Security</h2>
        <p>
            While no system can be guaranteed 100% secure, the App is designed without persistent user data storage,
            reducing privacy risk significantly.
        </p>

        <h2>9. Policy Updates</h2>
        <p>
            This Privacy Policy may be updated occasionally to reflect improvements or compliance needs.
            Updates will be reflected in the ‚ÄúLast updated‚Äù date above.
        </p>

        <h2>10. Contact</h2>
        <p>
            If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, you may contact the developer via:
        </p>

        <% if (contact) { %>
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:<%= contact %>"><%= contact %></a></p>
        <% } else { %>
            <p><strong>GitHub Repository:</strong> <a href="<%= gh %>"><%= gh %></a></p>
        <% } %>

    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <%= appName %>.
        Privacy-first, open-source, and built for fun dinner decisions.
    </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
